#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:239 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:245
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:250
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:271
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A Cathedral makes 3 unhappy citizens content in a city, making it easier to "
"maintain order in that city. However, it does not affect citizens made "
"unhappy by military activity. The discovery of Theology increases the effect "
"of a Cathedral, making an additional unhappy citizen content. The discovery "
"of Communism lessens the effect of a Cathedral, reducing by one the number "
"of unhappy citizens made content."
msgstr ""
"أي - الحرف الأوّل في الأبجديّة اللّاتينيّة كاثدرائية الـ اللاهوت كاثدرائية "
"مواطنيين الـ الشيوعية كاثدرائية."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:267 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:273
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:278
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"City Walls make it easier to defend a city. They triple the defense strength "
"of units within the city against land and helicopter units. They are "
"ineffective against airborne and sea units as well as Howitzers. City Walls "
"also prevent the loss of population which occurs when a defending unit is "
"destroyed by a land unit."
msgstr "المدينة الحوائط هم هم المدينة الحوائط وحدات وحدات."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:276 data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:358
#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:282 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:287
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:308 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:391
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:355
