msgstr "دفاع ساحلي"

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:293 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:299
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:304
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:325
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Increases the defense strength of units within a city by a factor of 2 when "
"defending against bombardments from enemy ships."
msgstr "الزيادات."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:315
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Entertains the citizens of a city, making 3 unhappy citizens content (four "
"after the discovery of Electronics). However, it does not affect citizens "
"made unhappy by military activity."
msgstr "يسلّي أربعة الالكترونيات"

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the corruption and waste in a city by 50%, and makes the revolt cost "
"of the city 4 times bigger. These effects are redundant in your capital city."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:343
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Under a Democracy, a Courthouse also makes 1 unhappy citizen content, unless "
"that citizen is unhappy about military activity."
msgstr "يخفّض تحت الحكم الديقراطي محكمة مواطنيين أيضًا."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:398 data/civ2civ3/buildings.ruleset:494
#: data/classic/buildings.ruleset:406 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:413
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:404 data/royale/buildings.ruleset:526
#: data/sandbox/buildings.ruleset:489
msgid "Harbor"
msgstr "مرفأ"

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:416 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:424
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:431
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:422
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Gives one extra food resource on all Oceanic tiles. The city needs to be "
"coastal to build this improvement."
msgstr "يعطي الطعام المحيط الـ."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:448
msgid ""
"A city can only have one Power Plant, Hydro Plant, Nuclear Plant, or Solar "
"Plant.  A city can only build a Hydro Plant if it is next to (or on) a River "
"tile."
msgstr ""

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:517 data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:585
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Neutralizes the pollution generated by the population. The population simply "
"has no effect on the pollution generated in the city."
msgstr "يحيّد الـ."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:542 data/classic/buildings.ruleset:553
#: data/experimental/buildings.ruleset:613
#: data/multiplayer/buildings.ruleset:548
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Together with a Factory, a Manufacturing Plant increases the shield "
"production in a city by 100%. A Manufacturing Plant on its own increases "
"shield production by 50%."
msgstr "سوية مع مصنع التصنيع النبات درع."

#: data/civ2/buildings.ruleset:567
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reduces the amount of pollution generated by production in a city by 50%. It "
"also increases the shield production of a Factory or Mfg. Plant in the city. "
"A Factory and a Nuclear Plant together give a 100% production bonus, and a "
"Factory, Mfg. Plant and Nuclear Plant together give a 150% production bonus."
msgstr ""
"يخفّض هو درع مصنع النبات مصنع نووي النبات مصنع النبات نووي النبات المصحة "
